entries.allies_arrived: Your fleet has arrived young one, take command.
entries.allies_remain: Imperial Pilot: < Massive da..ge sust...ed to critic... >
entries.battle_started: Annihilate them all. Don't disappoint me.
entries.enemies_arrived: The enemy is here, prepare yourself.
entries.enemies_remain: Imperial Squadron Leader: < Threat eliminated. %DI more to go. >
entries.enemies_win: It would appear my trust in your abilities was misplaced. Return immediately.
entries.found_loc: Proceed to this location immediately. Do not fail me young one.
entries.quest_findbattle_d: Meet up with the Imperial fleet at these coordinates.
entries.quest_helpallies_d: Lord Vader has put you in command of the attack. You best not disappoint him.
entries.quest_location_d: The Kashyyyk system is not heavily controlled by any force. Beware of pirates, over ambitious slavers and in this case, Rebels.
entries.split_quest_alert: Lord Vader: < Their transports are yours young one, destroy them. >
entries.title: Kashyyyk system: Defeating an invasion.
entries.title_d: The Rebel Alliance is moving a fleet of troops to the planet of Kashyyyk in an attempt to liberate it from slavery and Imperial influence. Lead a fleet of Imperial fighters to first breach through the Rebel fighter defense and then to destroy the troop transports.
